social_posts.post_text: Sketchbook finished! Stay tuned…. Will be selling a book of my sketches soon.
Might be taking on more refrigerator portrait commissions soon. Stay tuned.
Queen Liliʻuokalani drawing I’m donating for @gallerynucleus ‘s charity art show. Be sure to check it out this Sunday. Lots of great artists on the list. Doors open at 3, sales begin at 5.
My next book was announced on Publishers Weekly. A very important story that needs to be told. Stay tuned.
